All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
chartDisplayController
This is the controller class for the window displaying visualizations of the distribution of planets and resources among all factions.
Faction
This class holds information about a faction within the game.
Launcher
This class enables the application to be exported to a JAR executable on devices without JavaFX installed separately.
mainMenuController
This is the controller class for the main window in which the player selects which of the program's three main functions is to be used next.
Map
This class holds information about the game's entire map, and the import method to construct it.
MAPP
This application calculates routes, assesses threats, and selects targets for players in the tabletop roleplaying/strategy game Nexus.
Planet
This class holds data about an individual planet.
RouteCalculator
This class calculates routes and holds the resulting information to be accessed by other classes.
routeDisplayController
This is the controller class for the window in which the calculated route is displayed.
routeInfoController
This is the controller class for the window in which information used to calculate routes is entered.
selectFactionController
This is the controller class for the preliminary window in which the player selects their faction.
targetChartController
This is the controller class for the window displaying a visualization of target priorities.
targetDisplayController
This is the controller class for the window in which prioritized targets are displayed.
targetInfoController
This is the controller class for the window in which information used to select targets is entered.
TargetSelector
This class selects the most advantageous targets given the scenario information provided, ranking them and holding the list for use by other classes.
threatChartController
This is the controller class for the window displaying a visualization of threat probabilities.
threatDisplayController
This is the controller class for the window in which identified vulnerabilities are displayed and ranked.
threatInfoController
This is the controller class for the window in which information used to assess the player's vulnerabilities is entered.
